📊 SUMMARY OF MODERN SPRING MODULITH
Concept	How It Works
Define Module	@ApplicationModule in package-info.java
Publish Event	ApplicationEventPublisher.publishEvent()
Listen to Event	@ApplicationModuleListener (async + transactional built-in!)
Share a Service	Add @Service annotation → other modules can import!
Share a Repository	Add @Repository annotation → other modules can import!
Share a Controller	Add @RestController annotation → other modules can import!
Share a Component	Add @Component annotation → other modules can import!

// ✅ ANY Spring bean can be imported by other modules!

